/pitfall2-1200x842.png 1200w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/pitfall2-1400x982.png 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1982px) 100vw, 1982px\" /></figure></div></div><div class=\"gb-profile-column gb-profile-content-wrap\"><h2 class=\"gb-profile-name\" style=\"color:#32373c\">Avoid these 3 Data Migration Pitfalls</h2><p class=\"gb-profile-title\" style=\"color:#32373c\"><a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/sfdc_migration_issues/\" title=\"3 Common Salesforce.com Data Migration Issues to Avoid\"><strong>Read Article</strong></a></p><div class=\"gb-profile-text\"><p></p></div><ul class=\"gb-social-links\"></ul></div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover gb-block-cta\" style=\"padding-top:2%;min-height:13em;aspect-ratio:unset;\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\" style=\"background-color:#f1f2f2\"></span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#32373c;font-size:32;line-height:1\"><strong>Get access to our Salesforce data migration tool</strong>!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color\" style=\"color:#32373c;line-height:1\">We would love to learn about your data migration, management and analytics challenges.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-16018d1d wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-font-size gb-block-button\" style=\"font-size:26px;line-height:1.8\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-text-color has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"/beta\" style=\"border-radius:5px;color:#ffffff;background-color:#1ee2b0;padding-top:10px;padding-right:1.2em;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:1.2em\">Get Started!</a></div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div><